Jeonbuk National University: Jeonbuk National University (JBNU; Korean, 전북대학교, Jeonbuk Daehakgyo) is one of ten Flagship Korean National Universities founded in 1947, located in Jeonju, South Korea. Jeonbuk National University has been ranked 551–560th in the world by QS Top Universities Ranking in 2023.[1]
